    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >面对入侵你池塘的虫群，与它们对抗，并享受美味的零食吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你决定冒险故事的走向，选择下一章并决定接下来的发展，通过制定策略尽可能多地吞下苍蝇。在两轮游戏之间，你可以在商店里使用辛苦赚来的“青蛙币”，以更强大的状态开启下一轮冒险！在你讲述的众多故事中，你将发现新的舌头，找到有用的物品，解锁新的可用青蛙，并开启新的章节，让你的故事朝着意想不到的方向发展。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>特征</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 在地图上移动，躲避强大的敌人，吞吃弱小的敌人  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 升级并明智地选择强化内容，实施你的策略以推进进程  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 选择下一章，讲述属于你的故事  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 收集青蛙币并购买道具来增强未来的游戏体验  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 探索新的舌头、物品、章节和角色</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>吃虫子</strong>  </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315020/extras/2c1e85656f3c6dfdf3c3792e2b86bc37.poster.avif?t=1745413411\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315020/extras/2c1e85656f3c6dfdf3c3792e2b86bc37.webm?t=1745413411\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315020/extras/2c1e85656f3c6dfdf3c3792e2b86bc37.mp4?t=1745413411\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>多吃虫子</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315020/extras/84e5b066d31d6dc22659a51403a7ed7e.poster.avif?t=1745413411\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315020/extras/84e5b066d31d6dc22659a51403a7ed7e.webm?t=1745413411\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315020/extras/84e5b066d31d6dc22659a51403a7ed7e.mp4?t=1745413411\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>成为最好的青蛙</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315020/extras/4a43900663212076765c872db0a9721d.poster.avif?t=1745413411\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315020/extras/4a43900663212076765c872db0a9721d.webm?t=1745413411\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315020/extras/4a43900663212076765c872db0a9721d.mp4?t=1745413411\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>结交新朋友</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315020/extras/59b686bf2ac80fb8a4b0b55aeef4b90a.poster.avif?t=1745413411\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315020/extras/59b686bf2ac80fb8a4b0b55aeef4b90a.webm?t=1745413411\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315020/extras/59b686bf2ac80fb8a4b0b55aeef4b90a.mp4?t=1745413411\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>为你的下一次冒险做好准备</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315020/extras/874f1743df9bc81169462ffd0a49dbcb.gif?t=1745413411\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315020/extras/874f1743df9bc81169462ffd0a49dbcb.poster.avif?t=1745413411\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span></p>",
